'''Aglim''' d [[agman]] iy teddlen [[tafekka talsant]] d [[tafekka|tfekkiwin]] n waṭas n [[aɣersiw|iɣersiwen]] niden.<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Alibardi L | year = 2003 | title = Adaptation to the land: The skin of reptiles in comparison to that of amphibians and endotherm amniotes | url = | journal = J Exp Zoolog B Mol Dev Evol. | volume = 298 | issue = 1| pages = 12–41 | doi = 10.1002/jez.b.24 | pmid = 12949767 }}</ref><ref>{{amnir n wedlis|akala= https://books.google.com/?id=UklQAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA635&lpg=PA635&dq=necturus+integument+google+book#v=onepage&q=necturus%20integument%20google%20book&f=false|azwel=Journal of Morphology|adlis=1920-01-01|anefsar=Wistar Institute of Anatomy and Biology .|tutlayt=en|akala n ufaylu= https://web.archive.org/web/20200126111151/https://books.google.com/?id=UklQAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA635&lpg=PA635&dq=necturus+integument+google+book#v=onepage&q=necturus%20integument%20google%20book&f=false|azmez n ufaylu=2020-01-26}}</ref><ref>[http://pharmaxchange.info/press/2011/03/the-ageing-skin-part-1-structure-of-skin-and-introduction/ The Ageing Skin – Structure]. pharmaxchange.info. March 3, 2011 {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717201009/http://pharmaxchange.info/press/2011/03/the-ageing-skin-part-1-structure-of-skin-and-introduction/ |date=17 yulyu 2017}}</ref> Tawuri tagejdant n weglim ɣer [[Afgan|wemdan]] d taggaẓt n tfekka anda iga d azerrig n westan amenzu mgal ibiktiren, Aglim iteggeẓ tafekka s iylan-is [[Tasengama|imsengamen]] acku aglem yettili mgal abezzug akken iy geddel anekcum n [[amazzal|imazzalen]] s agensu n tfekka, Dɣa aglim iga d agman meqqren yakk di tfekka.

Aglim igeddel (ur yettaǧǧa ara) [[Tabintirt|tibiktirin]] d [[tanga takrurant|tnegwa tikruranin]] ad kecment ar umur ameqran n tfekka akken yettaggaẓ izeṭṭiwen id yezgan s ddaw-is seg [[azenzar|izenzaren]] n tfukt.

S tmerniwt ar wanect-a yakk, aglim yettalel deg waray n [[taẓɣelt|teẓɣelt]] n ugensu n tfekka deg yiswiren-is imazgayen. Anecta yettili-d s usufeɣ n [[tidi]] sɣur [[Awles|iwelsen]] yellan s ddaw n weglim mi ara tali teẓɣelt n tfekka. And [[Arugen|tetriget]] tidi ayen i d-igellun s tesmeṭ n tfekka.

Llant 3 n tissiwin tigejdanin deg weglim:
* [[Taglimt]]: d tissi tuffiɣt, tissi ayyi tla (tesɛa) [[tabniqt|tikwatin]] n  [[Milanin]] igan d tagensast ɣef yini n teglimt 
* [[Adu-glim]]: Tuffirt n weglim s ddaw n teglimt. Deg-s tiggariwin tinessurin d iwelsen n tidu
* Azeṭṭa adu-glim: Deg-s tikwatin n tassemt.

